data.name: Hotel Renato
data.description:
Hotel Renato is an excellent choice for travelers visiting Sesto San Giovanni, offering many helpful amenities designed to enhance your stay.
Given the close proximity of popular landmarks, such as Ex Monastero di San Nicolao (0.3 mi) and Monumento ai Caduti (0.4 mi), guests of Hotel Renato can easily experience some of Sesto San Giovanni's most well known attractions.
Free wifi is offered to guests, and rooms at Hotel Renato offer a flat screen TV, air conditioning, and a minibar.
Guests of Hotel Renato are also welcome to enjoy a lounge, located on site.
While in Sesto San Giovanni be sure to experience local oyster favorites at Osteria del Riccio.
Plus, during your trip, don’t forget to check out some of the popular historic sites, such as Villa Visconti d'Aragona, Villa Mylius VonWiller, and Villa Puricelli Guerra, Marelli.
Enjoy your stay in Sesto San Giovanni!

Close to some of Milan's most popular landmarks, such as Bosco Verticale (1.6 mi) and Monumental Cemetery (1.7 mi), Villa Lia is a great destination for tourists.
The inn features a 24 hour front desk and baggage storage, and you can stay connected during your stay as Villa Lia offers guests free internet access. Plus, Villa Lia offers an on-site restaurant, providing a pleasant respite from your busy day. For guests with a vehicle, free parking is available.
Travelers looking to enjoy some falafel can head to Ristorante Aladino or NUN Taste of Middle East. Otherwise, you may want to check out an Italian restaurant such as Alessandro Borghese - Il Lusso della Semplicita, Ceresio 7 Pools & Restaurant, or Risoelatte.
